4_H_Procedures_8: I only said AI generator because this response was clear, complete sentences.  A doctor who was taking the time to write out the response (rather than maybe using a voice to text app?) could also have produced a response that looks like this

5_L_Conditions_8: I have been assigning responses in complete sentences to the AI generator, but I think here that maybe the AI would have made a point of responding to the part of the question about medication. 1_L_Diagnostics_8: Again, this could either be a doctor who is taking the time to write in complete sentences, or it is an AI
3_L_Recovery_8: This could really be from either source.  I'm assuming doctor since there is a reason given for each point of the aftercare.  I'm guessing that an AI would only answer with the list of what the points are but not the purpose for them
